{"product_id":"bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Hand and Body Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing hand and body cream, soft and scented, exquisite for dry, reddened and in need of attention skin. Enriched with oils, vitamins, propoli and organic honey, it nourishes your skin making it supple, radiant and fragrant. Soft and light like a caress, it removes daily stress and promotes a pleasant feeling of relaxation in every part of your body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Use every day after a shower or bath on dry skin. Apply all over the body and massage gently until completely absorbed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Glyceryl stearate SE, Cetearyl alcohol, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Parfum, Glycerin, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tocopheryl acetate, Mel*, Propolis, Coumarin, Limonene, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Linalool, Geraniol, Isoeugenol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245324169543,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml-5351249.png?v=1756636043","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}